===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|ar|الْقُرْآن}}, definite form of {{m|ar|قُرْآن||act of reciting}}, verbal noun of {{m|ar|قَرَأَ||to recite; to read (aloud)}}. (The obsolete alternative spellings with "''al-''", like {{m|en|Alcoran|the Alcoran}}, redundantly retained the Arabic definite article.) Compare {{cog|syc|ܩܪܝܢܐ||tr=qeryānā|reading; scripture}}.

